{"type": "article", "id": 25138, "title": "探索多种材料的凳子", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-08T07:02:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607113224WMSPJftjYF41x3cT.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这些彩色的凳子来自以色列设计师 Maor Aharon 的计划“matter of motion”，他试图探索材料、运动和形状之间的关系。座位本身使用了聚合树脂，在铸造过程加入金属和木材等不同材料，形成了不一样的颜色和质感，同时方形的座位本身层层加入圆形或者拱形的纹路，很绚丽。四根腿则也使用了木材、黄铜和金属等不同材料，使至多变且有年轻的气息。<a href=\"http://maoraharon.com/#Home\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113221mNVZ1SK2Y8xTDLp9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.28796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113222xA5K4qLaFCVR7sdY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.26759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113222lwk3tJeGFf8CauI2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071132236qhTb5K04Hf1mYGl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113223vRETIaF1UZtphPmS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41442543\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}